    "body": "by the way, a simple workaround for this is to parenthesize the `match` expression:\n\n``` rust\nfn bool_to_i32(val: bool) -> i32 {\n  (match val {\n    true => 1i32,\n    false => 0i32\n  }) as i32\n}\n\nfn main() {}\n```\n",
